{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"g001infrastructure","type":"group","x":-100,"y":1100,"width":2200,"height":320,"label":"🏗️ Infrastructure Layer 基础设施层","color":"6"},
		{"id":"g002foundation","type":"group","x":-100,"y":720,"width":2200,"height":340,"label":"🧠 Foundation Models 基础模型层","color":"5"},
		{"id":"g003framework","type":"group","x":-100,"y":340,"width":2200,"height":340,"label":"⚙️ Framework & Orchestration 框架编排层","color":"4"},
		{"id":"g004tools","type":"group","x":-100,"y":-40,"width":2200,"height":340,"label":"🔧 Tools & Integration 工具集成层","color":"2"},
		{"id":"g005application","type":"group","x":-100,"y":-440,"width":2200,"height":360,"label":"🚀 Application Layer 应用层","color":"1"},
		{"id":"n001cloud","type":"text","x":0,"y":1180,"width":280,"height":180,"text":"# ☁️ Cloud Providers\n\n- **AWS** (Bedrock, SageMaker)\n- **Azure** (OpenAI Service)\n- **GCP** (Vertex AI)\n- **阿里云** (通义系列)\n\n`按需扩展 | 全球部署`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"n002compute","type":"text","x":320,"y":1180,"width":280,"height":180,"text":"# 🖥️ GPU/TPU 算力\n\n- **NVIDIA** H100/A100\n- **Google TPU** v5p\n- **AMD** MI300X\n- **华为** 昇腾 910B\n\n`推理加速 | 训练集群`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"n003vectordb","type":"text","x":640,"y":1180,"width":280,"height":180,"text":"# 🗄️ Vector Database\n\n- **Pinecone** (托管服务)\n- **Milvus** (开源分布式)\n- **Qdrant** (Rust高性能)\n- **Chroma** (轻量嵌入式)\n\n`向量检索 | 语义搜索`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"n004storage","type":"text","x":960,"y":1180,"width":280,"height":180,"text":"# 💾 Data & Storage\n\n- **S3/OSS** 对象存储\n- **Redis** 缓存层\n- **PostgreSQL** + pgvector\n- **OpenSearch** 全文+向量\n\n`数据湖 | 混合检索`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"n005observ","type":"text","x":1280,"y":1180,"width":280,"height":180,"text":"# 📊 Observability\n\n- **LangSmith** 调试追踪\n- **Helicone** 代理监控\n- **Prometheus** 指标\n- **OpenTelemetry** 链路\n\n`Token统计 | 成本分析`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"n006gateway","type":"text","x":1600,"y":1180,"width":280,"height":180,"text":"# 🌐 API Gateway\n\n- **LiteLLM** 统一代理\n- **OpenRouter** 路由聚合\n- **Portkey** 可靠性网关\n- **Kong** API管理\n\n`负载均衡 | 故障转移`","color":"6"},
		{"id":"n007gpt","type":"text","x":0,"y":800,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🤖 OpenAI 系列\n\n| 模型 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **GPT-4o** | 多模态旗舰 |\n| **GPT-4.1** | 推理增强 |\n| **o1/o3** | 深度思考 |\n\n```\n128K context | Function Call\n```","color":"5"},
		{"id":"n008claude","type":"text","x":360,"y":800,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🎭 Anthropic Claude\n\n| 模型 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **Opus 4.5** | 超强推理 |\n| **Sonnet 4** | 速度均衡 |\n| **Haiku** | 极速响应 |\n\n```\n200K context | Extended Think\n```","color":"5"},
		{"id":"n009gemini","type":"text","x":720,"y":800,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 💎 Google Gemini\n\n| 模型 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **Ultra 2.5** | 多模态王者 |\n| **Pro 2.5** | 生产主力 |\n| **Flash** | 闪电推理 |\n\n```\n1M context | Grounding\n```","color":"5"},
		{"id":"n010opensource","type":"text","x":1080,"y":800,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🦙 开源模型\n\n| 模型 | 参数 |\n|------|------|\n| **Llama 3.3** | 70B |\n| **Qwen 2.5** | 72B |\n| **DeepSeek V3** | MoE |\n\n```\n本地部署 | 微调友好\n```","color":"5"},
		{"id":"n011embed","type":"text","x":1440,"y":800,"width":280,"height":200,"text":"# 🔢 Embedding 模型\n\n- **text-embedding-3**\n- **voyage-3**\n- **bge-m3** (多语言)\n- **jina-embeddings-v3**\n\n```\n3072维 | 语义向量化\n```","color":"5"},
		{"id":"n012multimodal","type":"text","x":1760,"y":800,"width":280,"height":200,"text":"# 🎨 多模态模型\n\n- **DALL·E 3** 图像生成\n- **Sora** 视频生成\n- **Whisper** 语音识别\n- **ElevenLabs** TTS\n\n```\n视觉理解 | 内容生成\n```","color":"5"},
		{"id":"n013langchain","type":"text","x":0,"y":420,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🦜 LangChain\n\n**最流行的 LLM 应用框架**\n\n- Chains (链式调用)\n- Agents (智能代理)\n- Memory (对话记忆)\n- Callbacks (回调钩子)\n\n`Python | TypeScript`","color":"4"},
		{"id":"n014llamaindex","type":"text","x":360,"y":420,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🦙 LlamaIndex\n\n**数据框架专家**\n\n- Data Connectors\n- Index Structures\n- Query Engines\n- Response Synthesis\n\n`RAG首选 | 知识库`","color":"4"},
		{"id":"n015agentsdk","type":"text","x":720,"y":420,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🤖 Agent SDK\n\n**下一代 Agent 框架**\n\n- **Claude Agent SDK**\n- **OpenAI Agents SDK**\n- **AutoGen** (微软)\n- **CrewAI** (多智能体)\n\n`自主决策 | 工具调用`","color":"4"},
		{"id":"n016mcp","type":"text","x":1080,"y":420,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🔌 MCP 协议\n\n**Model Context Protocol**\n\n- Tools (工具能力)\n- Resources (资源访问)\n- Prompts (提示模板)\n- Sampling (采样控制)\n\n`标准化 | 可扩展`","color":"4"},
		{"id":"n017sglang","type":"text","x":1440,"y":420,"width":280,"height":200,"text":"# ⚡ Inference Engine\n\n- **vLLM** 高吞吐\n- **SGLang** 结构化生成\n- **TensorRT-LLM**\n- **llama.cpp** 边缘\n\n`KV缓存 | 批处理`","color":"4"},
		{"id":"n018workflow","type":"text","x":1760,"y":420,"width":280,"height":200,"text":"# 🔄 Workflow Engine\n\n- **Dify** 可视化编排\n- **Flowise** 低代码\n- **n8n** 自动化\n- **Temporal** 编排\n\n`DAG流程 | 人机协作`","color":"4"},
		{"id":"n019rag","type":"text","x":0,"y":40,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 📚 RAG 系统\n\n**检索增强生成**\n\n```mermaid\nQuery → Retrieve → Augment → Generate\n```\n\n- 语义切片 | 混合检索\n- Rerank重排 | 上下文压缩\n- GraphRAG | 知识图谱","color":"2"},
		{"id":"n020function","type":"text","x":360,"y":40,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🛠️ Function Calling\n\n**工具调用能力**\n\n```json\n{\n  \"name\": \"search\",\n  \"arguments\": {...}\n}\n```\n\n- 结构化输出\n- 并行调用\n- 错误恢复","color":"2"},
		{"id":"n021mcpserver","type":"text","x":720,"y":40,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🔧 MCP Servers\n\n**热门工具服务**\n\n| 类型 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| 文件 | filesystem |\n| 搜索 | brave, exa |\n| 代码 | github |\n| 数据 | postgres |","color":"2"},
		{"id":"n022memory","type":"text","x":1080,"y":40,"width":320,"height":200,"text":"# 🧠 Memory 记忆系统\n\n**长短期记忆管理**\n\n- **Buffer** 短期缓存\n- **Summary** 摘要压缩\n- **Entity** 实体追踪\n- **Vector** 语义记忆\n\n`个性化 | 持久化`","color":"2"},
		{"id":"n023guardrails","type":"text","x":1440,"y":40,"width":280,"height":200,"text":"# 🛡️ Guardrails\n\n**安全护栏**\n\n- 输入验证\n- 输出过滤\n- 毒性检测\n- 幻觉检查\n\n`合规 | 可信AI`","color":"2"},
		{"id":"n024eval","type":"text","x":1760,"y":40,"width":280,"height":200,"text":"# 📏 Evaluation\n\n**评估框架**\n\n- **RAGAS** RAG评估\n- **DeepEval** 单元测试\n- **promptfoo** 提示测试\n- **LMSys** 竞技场\n\n`基准测试 | A/B实验`","color":"2"},
		{"id":"n025coding","type":"text","x":0,"y":-360,"width":380,"height":240,"text":"# 💻 AI 编程助手\n\n**代码生成 | 智能补全 | 重构**\n\n| 产品 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **Cursor** | IDE深度集成 |\n| **Claude Code** | CLI Agent |\n| **GitHub Copilot** | 生态完善 |\n| **Windsurf** | 流式编辑 |\n\n`Agentic Coding | Vibe Coding`","color":"1"},
		{"id":"n026chatbot","type":"text","x":420,"y":-360,"width":380,"height":240,"text":"# 💬 AI 对话助手\n\n**问答 | 创作 | 分析**\n\n| 产品 | 公司 |\n|------|------|\n| **ChatGPT** | OpenAI |\n| **Claude.ai** | Anthropic |\n| **Gemini** | Google |\n| **Kimi** | 月之暗面 |\n\n`多模态 | 联网搜索`","color":"1"},
		{"id":"n027autonomous","type":"text","x":840,"y":-360,"width":380,"height":240,"text":"# 🤖 自主 Agent\n\n**规划 | 执行 | 反思**\n\n| 产品 | 能力 |\n|------|------|\n| **Devin** | 软件工程 |\n| **AutoGPT** | 通用任务 |\n| **BabyAGI** | 任务分解 |\n| **MetaGPT** | 多角色协作 |\n\n`自我迭代 | 工具编排`","color":"1"},
		{"id":"n028search","type":"text","x":1260,"y":-360,"width":340,"height":240,"text":"# 🔍 AI 搜索引擎\n\n**深度研究 | 多源整合**\n\n| 产品 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **Perplexity** | 对话式搜索 |\n| **Grok** | 实时推特 |\n| **秘塔AI** | 深度搜索 |\n\n`引用溯源 | 知识图谱`","color":"1"},
		{"id":"n029vertical","type":"text","x":1640,"y":-360,"width":340,"height":240,"text":"# 🏢 垂直领域 Agent\n\n**专业场景深度定制**\n\n| 领域 | 应用 |\n|------|------|\n| 法律 | Harvey AI |\n| 医疗 | Med-PaLM |\n| 金融 | Bloomberg GPT |\n| 客服 | Intercom Fin |\n\n`领域知识 | 合规安全`","color":"1"},
		{"id":"n030title","type":"text","x":700,"y":-580,"width":600,"height":100,"text":"# 🌌 AI Agent 技术生态全景图\n\n**From Infrastructure to Intelligence | 2025**","color":"#7c3aed"},
		{"id":"n031legend","type":"text","x":2150,"y":400,"width":260,"height":350,"text":"# 📋 图例\n\n---\n\n🔴 **应用层**\n用户直接交互\n\n🟠 **工具集成层**\n能力扩展\n\n🟢 **框架编排层**\n开发抽象\n\n🔵 **基础模型层**\n智能核心\n\n🟣 **基础设施层**\n底层支撑\n\n---\n\n`→ 数据/控制流向`","color":"#374151"},
		{"id":"n032dataflow","type":"text","x":2150,"y":800,"width":260,"height":200,"text":"# 🔄 典型调用链\n\n```\n用户输入\n   ↓\n应用层处理\n   ↓\n工具调用/RAG\n   ↓\n框架编排\n   ↓\nLLM推理\n   ↓\n基础设施\n```","color":"#374151"}
	],
